AggOO::GdiplusStartupInput

AggOO::GdiplusStartupInput Struct Reference

#include <AggOOInit.h>

Detailed Description

Remarks:
GDI+ requires initialization routines, but AGG does not. Since the idea of AggOO is to be able to replace GDI+ by simply changing the namespace, these "initialization" methods and structures are provided. They actually do nothing (since AggOO does not require any extra initializing) and are merely present for the cases of converting GDI+ -> AggOO. Space-holder
